entry.dataset_id: Sentinel-6A MF Jason-CS L2 P4 Altimeter Low Resolution (LR) NRT Ocean Surface Topography
entry.title: Sentinel-6A MF Jason-CS L2 P4 Altimeter Low Resolution (LR) NRT Ocean Surface Topography
entry.summary: Provides low resolution (LR) near real time (NRT; 3-hour latency) measurements of sea surface height anomaly (SSHA), Significant Wave Height (SWH), and Wind Speed, along with 1 Hz and 20 Hz measurements from the radar altimeter, orbit altitude, environmental range corrections, instrument corrections, and geophysical models. The NRT product is analogous to the Jason-3 OGDR product.

entry.dataset_id: MISR Near Real Time (NRT) Level 1B2 Ellipsoid Data V001
entry.title: MISR Near Real Time (NRT) Level 1B2 Ellipsoid Data V001
entry.summary: This file contains Ellipsoid-projected TOA Radiance,resampled at the surface and topographically corrected, as well as geometrically corrected by PGE22.  It is used for MISR Near Real Time processing, and is derived from session-based Level 0 input files.
